            <h2 class="h2">A COP26 presence in Glasgow highlights land rights, traditional knowledge, and the protection of life.</h2>
            <p>The Global Alliance of Territorial Communities (GATC) &mdash; a political platform of indigenous peoples and local communities &mdash; represents 35 million people living in forest territories from 24 countries in Asia, Africa, and Latin America, covering over 958 million hectares of land.</p>
            <p>Good Praxis were approached to design the stand and ...</p>
            <p>This was an international effort.</p>
            <p>To help me visualise scale, I made a 1:1 paper mockup in our Finsbury Park studio. This was a rough-and-ready. I document everything yet I don’t have any photos of this sadly!</p>
            <p>Brand foundations were set by Purpose’s São Paulo team.</p>
